  "title": "Staff Nurse - Specialist Clinic (Oncology) - Up to $4.5k [0580]",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>5.25 days; Mon – Fri 8.30am to 5.30pm, Alt Saturday: 8.30am to 1pm</li>\n  <li>Location: Mt.E Novena / Mt. E Orchard / Gleneagles Hospital / Mount Alvernia Hospital (To be discuss during interview)</li>\n  <li>Salary: $3000 - $4500</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong> Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist with the provision of nursing care for patients on chemotherapy</li>\n  <li>Assisting with initial health assessment of patient</li>\n  <li>Observing and recording the condition of patients;</li>\n  <li>Checking, dispensing and administering drugs and injections;</li>\n  <li>Responding to emergencies;</li>\n  <li>Communicating with and relieving the anxiety of patients and their relatives;</li>\n  <li>Educating patients about their health;</li>\n  <li>Maintaining patient records;</li>\n  <li>Assisting doctors in minor procedures</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Nursing</li>\n  <li>1-2 years of experience in the industry</li>\n  <li>Registered with the Singapore Nursing Board (SNB)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p>\n<p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
